<plot>You control Sketch Turner, a struggling comic book artist who falls into his own comic book creation one day, while drawing his favorite character Mortus. The two switch places, and the confused artist Sketch finds himself trapped in the world that he created. Now he must find and fight his way back to reality and showdown with his sinister creation, Mortus.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?112230</url></doc>
